5000|$|VELUX 5 Oceans Race - {{formerly}} known as the BOC Challenge and later the Around Alone, this race started in 1982 with 17 entries. It is a <b>single-handed</b> <b>race</b> around the world, originally with 4 legs but now with 3.|$|E
